tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE Quantum_Cryptographic_Data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    quantum_key VARCHAR(255),
    encrypted_data TEXT,
    decryption_key VARCHAR(255),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE quantum_analysis (
    analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    data_id INT,
    analysis_result TEXT,
    analysis_time TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY (data_id) REFERENCES quantum_data(id)
);

CREATE TABLE QuantumCryptographyData (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    quantum_key VARCHAR(100),
    encrypted_data VARCHAR(255),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE PatternIdentification (
    pattern_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    pattern_description TEXT,
    occurrence_count INT,
    analyzed_data_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (analyzed_data_id) REFERENCES QuantumCryptographyData(id)
)

CREATE TABLE TrendAnalysis (
    trend_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    trend_name VARCHAR(50),
    trend_description TEXT,
    analyzed_data_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (analyzed_data_id) REFERENCES QuantumCryptographyData(id)
)

CREATE TABLE QuantumComputer (
    qc_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    qc_name VARCHAR(50),
    manufacturer VARCHAR(100),
    performance_rating INT
)

CREATE TABLE Quantum_Cryptography_Data (
    data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    encoded_data TEXT,
    quantum_algorithm VARCHAR(50),
    analysis_result TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE Quantum_Key_Exchange (
    key_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    public_key TEXT,
    private_key TEXT,
    expiration_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE Quantum_Data_Analysis (
    analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    data_id INT,
    analysis_type VARCHAR(50),
    analysis_result TEXT,
    CONSTRAINT fk_data_id FOREIGN KEY(data_id) REFERENCES Quantum_Cryptography_Data(data_id)
)

CREATE TABLE Quantum_Data_Trends (
    trend_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    trend_name VARCHAR(50),
    trend_description TEXT,
    CONSTRAINT fk_analysis_id FOREIGN KEY(analysis_id) REFERENCES Quantum_Data_Analysis(analysis_id)
)

CREATE TABLE Quantum_Data_Patterns (
    pattern_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    pattern_name VARCHAR(50),
    pattern_description TEXT,
    CONSTRAINT fk_analysis_id FOREIGN KEY(analysis_id) REFERENCES Quantum_Data_Analysis(analysis_id)
)
